---
title: Blistered Tomato & Chicken Sausage Risotto with Whipped Ricotta & Lemon
description: You may want to refer to this recipe as, Risott-Oh! Italian chicken sausage creates a savory base for a deliciously creamy risotto, infused with cream cheese and herbs. But wait, there’s more! We add game-changing toppings of fluffy, lemon-kissed ricotta clouds, juicy, sweet charred tomato, and a shower of fresh parsley. Serve it up and wait for the oohing and aahing.
